<title>Unit test: informalequation.001</title>

<para>As an image first.</para>

<informalexample>
<equation xml:id="eq.fermat">
<title>Fermat's Last Theorem</title>
  <alt>x^n + y^n ≠ z^n ∀ n > 2</alt>
  <mediaobject>
    <imageobject>
      <imagedata fileref="../media/db5d_refeqn01.png"/>
    </imageobject>
  </mediaobject>
</equation>
</informalexample>

<para>But this one actually works better as a <tag>mathphrase</tag>.
Or at least it works if you have a reasonable set of fonts.</para>

<informalexample>
<equation xml:id="eq.fermat.mathphrase">
<title>Fermat's Last Theorem</title>
<mathphrase>x<superscript>n</superscript> + y<superscript>n</superscript>
≠ z<superscript>n</superscript> ∀ n > 2</mathphrase>
</equation>
</informalexample>

